text: Auguste Dussourd (born 16 February 1996 in Paris) is a French professional squash player.https://psaworldtour.com/rankings/world_tour As of May 2019, he was ranked number 77 in the world.http://www.squashinfo.com/players/5701-auguste-dussourd Dussourd currently studies at the University of Oxford. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:French male squash players
